  "case_desc": "复诊"
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 200 && response.body.code === 0) {
        client.global.set("test_case_id_b", response.body.data.case_id);
    }
%}


### 7. 医生A查看所有病例（测试隔离：只应看到“医生A的病人”）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cases/get
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_a}}


### 8. 医生B查看所有病例（测试隔离：只应看到“医生B的病人”）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cases/get
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_b}}


### 9. (可选测试越权隔离) 半路医生A尝试越权查看医生B的具体病例
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cases/get?case_id={{test_case_id_b}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_a}}


### 10. 为医生A的病例创建一次“医学检查单 (Study)”
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cases/{{test_case_id_a}}/study/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_a}}

{
  "studys": [
    {
      "study_time": "2026-03-18",
      "study_type": "XRAY",
      "study_desc": "胸部常规X光扫描"
    }
  ]
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 200 && response.body.code === 0) {
        if (response.body.data.study && response.body.data.study.length > 0) {
            client.global.set("test_study_id_a", response.body.data.study[0].studyId);
        }
    }
%}


### 11. 稍等或者暂时跳过此假意见插入步骤 (原有的 /api/v1/infer_result/add API不存在)
# 这一步之前仅仅是我想象的为您插入一段假诊断数据的模拟，但由于您的系统中获取的是AI真实推理结果，并没有这个单纯供写入诊断结果的接口。
# 如果想测试诊断，可以留待上传真实图片后在业务上由您的后台自动生或者去调用 `/api/v1/image/infer/{image_id}` 。
# POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/infer_result/add ...


### 12. 更新刚才医生A创建的病例信息
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cases/{{test_case_id_a}}/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_a}}

{
  "age": 46,
  "caseDesc": "常规体检，已出部分结果"
}


### 13. 获取指定单个病例的详细信息 (验证刚刚的更新)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cases/get?case_id={{test_case_id_a}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_a}}


### 14. 软删除医生A创建的检查单 (Study)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cases/{{test_case_id_a}}/study/{{test_study_id_a}}/delete
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_a}}


### 15. 删除医生A的整个病例 (清理测试数据)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cases/{{test_case_id_a}}/delete
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_a}}

